high_descs: Turn around, proceed to dresser across room.
Pick up pencil from behind cd on dresser.
Turn around, proceed across to nightstand.
Place pencil diagonal on nightstand, to the right of lamp and cup.
anns.task_desc: Move pencil from dresser to nightstand.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the end of the bed then turn right and walk to the dresser.
Pick up the red pen that's in front of you.
Turn around and take a step to your right then walk to the small night stand.
Turn on the light that's on the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a pen in lamp light.

high_descs: Turn around to face the black dresser.
Pick up the red directly above the CD on the dresser.
Turn around to walk across the room to the nightstand on the right side of the bed.
Set the red pen down on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Move a red pen from the dresser to the nightstand.
